<section class="card" id="mod3">
  <h2>3) Commits e mensagens</h2>
  <p class="lead">Mensagem boa = contexto + escopo + inten√ß√£o. Ajuda revis√£o e auditoria.</p>
  <div class="grid cols-2">
    <div>
      <h3>Padr√£o (Conventional Commits)</h3>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Tipo</th><th>Exemplo</th><th>Uso</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><code>feat:</code></td><td>feat(login): fluxo com OAuth</td><td>nova feature</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>fix:</code></td><td>fix(api): corrige CORS</td><td>bug fix</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>docs:</code></td><td>docs: melhora README</td><td>documenta√ß√£o</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>chore:</code></td><td>chore: atualiza deps</td><td>rotina</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>refactor:</code></td><td>refactor(core): simplifica</td><td>refatora√ß√£o</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3>Boas pr√°ticas √ó Erros comuns</h3>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th class="good">Fazer</th><th class="bad">Evitar</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Commits pequenos e at√¥micos</td><td>‚Äúmega-commit‚Äù com tudo</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Mensagens com porqu√™/impacto</td><td>‚Äúupdate stuff‚Äù, ‚Äúajustes‚Äù</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Referenciar issue/PR (#123)</td><td>Sem contexto de tarefa</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3>Exemplos</h3>
  <div class="btn-row"><button class="copy" data-target="c3">copiar</button></div>
  <pre id="c3"><code># bom
